  "body": "The goal of this issue is to remove the [relayXDomainMessages](https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/6c9b91dbe83e5f056fe05ea9ae0c9c4d694df8f7/integration-tests/test/shared/env.ts#L181) function from the integration tests. This function should no longer be necessary because it can be replaced by the `CrossChainMessenger` class exported by the Optimism SDK. \r\n\r\nHere you can see an example of a place where this function is being used:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/6c9b91dbe83e5f056fe05ea9ae0c9c4d694df8f7/integration-tests/test/native-eth.spec.ts#L192-L193\r\n\r\nHere's an example of how to use the SDK instead:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/6c9b91dbe83e5f056fe05ea9ae0c9c4d694df8f7/integration-tests/test/basic-l1-l2-communication.spec.ts#L77-L83\r\n\r\nAs always, feel free to ask questions here if anything is confusing!",
